# Demo Application

## Frontend

Comamnds to run the frontend locally:

```
npm i
npm run dev
```

## Backend

Steps to run the backend locally:

1- Copy `.env.example`, rename it to `.env` and replace the jwt secret wtih your won

2- run the following commands to start the server locally

```
npm i
npm run start:dev
```

3- you can check the api documentation using route `/api`

4- run the unit tests using

```
npm run test
```

4- run the end to end tests using

```
npm run test:e2e
```
